39:     //   2. split on `|` (pipe to less etc.),
40:     //   3. split on `&&` (cd-and-then pattern: `cd X && grep …`).
41:     // For (3) we take the LAST segment because the chain semantically
42:     // ends with the meaningful command — `cd ~/dir && cat README.md`
43:     // is "the cat is what produces output", not the cd.
